data.title: Barton Announces President’s and Dean’s Lists for 2023 Spring Semester
data.meta_description: WILSON, N.C. —June 20, 2023 — Barton College named 97 full-time undergraduate students to the President’s List and 424 full-time undergraduate students to the Dean’s List for spring semester 2023. President’s List students compiled a perfect 4.0 grade point average; Dean’s List students achieved a grade point average of 3.3 or better on a four-point
